# Update guide for JavaScript libraries

# vis-network
This lib is used to plot the knowledge graph.
https://visjs.github.io/vis-network/docs/network/
https://github.com/visjs/vis-network

Run "npm install vis-network"
Only the "dist" folder is kept, all other folders are deleted.

# vis-timeline
This lib is used to plot the chronology of knowledge elements.
https://visjs.github.io/vis-timeline/docs/timeline/
https://github.com/visjs/vis-timeline

Run "npm install vis-timeline"
Only the "standalone/umd" and "styles" folders are kept, all other folders are deleted.
Current version: 7.4.9

# jstree
This lib is used to plot the tree viewer of knowledge elements.
https://www.jstree.com/

Download jstree.js from "https://github.com/vakata/jstree/tree/master/dist"
Download style.css from "https://github.com/vakata/jstree/tree/master/dist/themes/default" 
Move style.css to css folder, rename it to jstree.css
Check if the following images are up-to-date in images folder: 32px.png, 40px.png, throbber.gif

# treant
Used to plot trees of knowledge elements.
https://fperucic.github.io/treant-js/

# echarts
Used to plot pie charts and boxplots in dashboard items.
https://echarts.apache.org/en/index.html

Run "npm install echarts" or download from https://github.com/apache/echarts/tree/master/dist
Download echarts.js and extension/dataTool.js